hemring Group PLC\">OTCPK:CMGMY</a>) with a buy rating. Since then, the stock has fallen 16% at the <a href=\"https://www.londonstockexchange.com/stock/CHG/chemring-group-plc/company-page\" rel=\"nofollow\">London Stock Exchange</a> where the listing has more liquidity. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745511-chemring-stock-tanks-upside-remains-on-double-digit-ebitda-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:15:51", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745513", "title": "Alibaba: The End Of New Retail As We Know It?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female Clothing store retail display in shopping mall with discount sales tag\" data-id=\"1446944883\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76